<item>
            <title>[LU-6627] Client inode close failed: ll_close_inode_openhandle())</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-6627</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Several of the error happened during MDT failover, while MDT haven&apos;t become available again:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;May 12 14:59:35 lola-23 kernel: LustreError: 23050:0:(file.c:172:ll_close_inode_openhandle()) inode 486389112580927253 mdc close failed: rc = -4
May 12 14:59:35 lola-23 kernel: LustreError: 23050:0:(file.c:172:ll_close_inode_openhandle()) Skipped 103 previous similar messages
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;No error messages can be correlated on OSS and MDT nodes.&lt;br/&gt;
user jobs weren&apos;t affected or crash by the error(s).&lt;/p&gt;</description>
